comments: This course offers an avenue to explore your individual interest in a formalized setting

I would definitely recommend the course to advanced Portuguese speakers. Just make sure you have a solid idea of what you want to focus on and a plan for what you envision on a weekly basis to make sure you get the most out of it.
Definitely try to do directed research in Portuguese. It's flexible and often interesting.
Take this course. Absolutely fantastic way to learn about a specific set of Portuguese vocabulary and really take your studies to an in-depth level.
Yes! It should be developed into a regular course!
